data.description: Newly refinished lfloora and fresh paint in living room and middle bedroom.  Nicely laid out home with wood floors throughout. Close to schools and Westfield shopping center. Formal dining room has built in cabinets and would make a fabulous home/office den, 2 Car Garage has heat and air in first stall. Attached workshop with water and drain access. Home has underground sprinklers, chain link fence, newer furnace and A/C. Storage Hutch/Cabinets may stay in bonus room. This is a Great Home and Ready for you!
